title: Strange: The Doctor Is Out
description: No longer Sorcerer Supreme of the Marvel Universe, Stephen Strange must discover a new path to fulfillment and enlightenment. Unfortunately, that path leads through a bizarre, terrifying gauntlet of magical menaces - and if the former Master of the Mystic Arts is going to survive the journey, he'll need some assistance - in the form of a brand-new student! Collects Strange #1-4.
author: Mark Waid
